And boom, we hit the curb.

00:12:04.322 --> 00:12:06.892
The car went up.

00:12:06.925 --> 00:12:09.094
I don't--honestly, I just went,
"Oh, my God.

00:12:09.127 --> 00:12:12.564
"Hey. What?

00:12:12.597 --> 00:12:13.999
What?"

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:19.104
I think I said, "Shit!"

00:12:19.137 --> 00:12:22.108
"Don't swear, Louie,
for God sakes."

00:12:24.776 --> 00:12:28.113
Yeah, we landed in the--
all the snow.

00:12:28.146 --> 00:12:30.215
Whoo!

00:12:30.248 --> 00:12:31.817
You know, it was we were--
I go,

00:12:31.850 --> 00:12:33.752
"This is like a snow globe.
This is like--

00:12:33.785 --> 00:12:38.590
We are--somebody's shaking us.
We're..."

